## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/secure-login-system.git
```

Open the project folder:

```bash
cd secure-login-system
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Run the Application

```bash
python app.py
```

Open in browser:

```text
